Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:44.37,通用720日文-ja,van,0,0,0,,なんで昔みたいに話せねんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.07,Default,van,0,0,0,,It's not that complicated...
