Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,For heaven's sake. You don't even drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:00:57.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ったく 飲めねぇくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:02.66,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's more complicated than you think.
