Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.71,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's called a piñata. Brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ピニャータってんだ 懐かしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.38,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.38,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,いい?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.97,Default,av,0,0,0,,Knock yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.97,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,勝手にしろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.53,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.53,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,ありがどう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.17,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.17,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,可愛いもんだら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Frate was a lot like that when he was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,フラテが小さかったころも あんな感じだったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:11.63,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,取れた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.74,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おい シスター
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.00,通用720日文-ja,sis,0,0,0,,はい 皆さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:25.01,Default,sis,0,0,0,,Everyone! This man has \Nsomething fun to show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.01,通用720日文-ja,sis,0,0,0,,今から 面白いものを見せていただけるそうですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.75,Default,sis,0,0,0,,Now, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.75,通用720日文-ja,sis,0,0,0,,では えって...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.42,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Marte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.42,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,マルテー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.25,Default,sis,0,0,0,,Fetch some balls for Mr. Marte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.25,通用720日文-ja,sis,0,0,0,,マルテーさんにボールを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.84,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go, here we go, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.84,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,さ 行くぞ行くぞ行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.96,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.96,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,はい よします
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.62,Default,kids,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.62,通用720日文-ja,kids,0,0,0,,かっこいい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.61,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Hey! What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.61,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,ねね こっちのお兄ちゃんは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:25.23,Default,kid,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:25.23,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,何やってくれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.12,Default,nero,0,0,0,,No use asking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.12,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,無理無理無理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.44,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Look at that gloomy, \Nsullen expression of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.44,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,面白みのない暗い顔してるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a scrap \Nof human kindness in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あいつは本当人間味のかけらもない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.41,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Is that mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:39.41,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺の?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.46,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What are you, a pickpocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.46,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ったく すりじゃあるまいし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.54,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.54,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おい 止めろって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.69,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.69,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.44,Overlap,kid,0,0,0,,He looks silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.44,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,{\an8}かっこ悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Making a fool out of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.29,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,出し物に使いやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.16,Default,av,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.16,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.24,Default,kids,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.24,通用720日文-ja,kids,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.05,Default,kids,0,0,0,,They were both really funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.05,通用720日文-ja,kids,0,0,0,,面白かった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.64,Default,kid,0,0,0,,You can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.64,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,これあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:13.48,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:13.48,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ほらよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:14.92,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:14.92,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.50,Default,kid,0,0,0,,You can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.50,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,はい これあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What the hell? It's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.16,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なんじゃこりゃあ ぼろぼろじゃねか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, it was cheap, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.20,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なぁ 安かったから いいけどよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You should start with just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まずは一個から練習すんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The trick is not to raise your hands too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.31,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,腕を上げすぎないのがこつだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Vanno was even better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:50.58,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ヴァンノは俺より上手かったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.94,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I was about ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.94,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,十歳の頃だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:06.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There was some circus troupe in \Ntown, the "Alexander" something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:06.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,アレキサンダーなんとかっていうサーカス団が町に来た
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Vanno and I really wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おれとヴァンノはどうしても行きたくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.66,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,日曜の礼拝を抜け出して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:15.43,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We slipped out of Sunday mass and \Nswiped some cash from Dad's wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.43,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,親父の財布から金を失敬した
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:20.37,Default,nero,0,0,0,,But Dad found out right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:20.37,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,でも あっさり親父にばれてな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He rearranged my face for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,顔の形が変わりまで ぶん殴られた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.34,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It sure was fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:27.34,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,けど 面白かった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Having something like that come \Nto a nothing town like ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:30.81,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なにもねぇ町にあんなのが来たんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:36.14,Default,nero,0,0,0,,For a while, we practiced together, \Njust like you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:36.14,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,さっきのお前みたいに しばらくは二人して練習してた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It was all we thought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.06,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まあ 夢中だったらな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:45.23,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Then we showed Frate and Fio, \Nand they went totally wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:45.23,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,で フラテとフィオに見せたら 狂ったように喜んだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.40,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Though they got bored pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.40,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,すぐに飽きられちまったけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.38,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You an only child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,孤児院育ちか?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.84,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.55,Default,av,0,0,0,,And then, as the cliché goes, \NI went on to become a gangster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.55,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,その後はお決まりのギャングまがいのガキだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.97,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That explains your little trick before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:00.97,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,それでさっきの腕前ってわけか?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.25,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You were a bad kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.25,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,悪いガキだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.56,Default,av,0,0,0,,My hands shook at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.56,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,初めは手が振えだけとな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.60,Default,av,0,0,0,,but now, they move before \NI even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.60,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,今じゃ 考える前に手が動く
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.29,Default,av,0,0,0,,What was your first job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.29,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あんたの初仕事は?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:20.72,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I went to lean on a guy who was \Nfilching money off the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:20.72,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ファミリーの金をくすねたやつを落としに行った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I was fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,十四の時だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.16,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,たしか...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.44,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Lagusa. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.44,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ラグーザとか言った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.24,Default,av,0,0,0,,You weren't alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.24,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,一人でじゃないよなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,There were four of us, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺を入れて4人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.34,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It was lousy work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.34,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,嫌な仕事だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.00,Default,av,0,0,0,,Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.00,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,殺したのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He made a move on us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.75,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,先に手を出したのは向こうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.77,Default,nero,0,0,0,,After that, there was no stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,その後は止めようがね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.21,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I shot at the kid who ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:52.21,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺は逃げたガキを撃った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.27,Default,nero,0,0,0,,but I didn't get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.27,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,だがやれなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.44,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That day, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.44,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あの時 俺は...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.82,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I've just \Nthrown myself into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.62,0:12:06.82,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あれから 我武者羅にやってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.16,Default,av,0,0,0,,And now you're a penniless runaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:11.16,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,で 今じゃ文無しの逃亡者ってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:14.71,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm a camper who does \Na little juggling on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:14.71,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,はあ ジャグリングもできるキャンパーか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.67,Default,av,0,0,0,,There was... one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.67,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もう一人 いた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.43,Default,guide,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.92,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You did that on purpose, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.92,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お前 絶対わざとだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.91,Default,av,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.91,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.15,Default,nero,0,0,0,,It's your turn to handle the shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:01.15,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ここの買い出しはお前の番だな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.85,Default,nick,0,0,0,,Not from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.85,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,余所者か?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.64,Default,nick,0,0,0,,If you wanna make trouble, do it elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.64,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,犯罪は他でやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.55,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.55,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あ そうだなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.50,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I doubt there's anything here\NI'd want to take, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.50,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,とりてぇもんは なんもなさそうだしな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.64,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're out of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.64,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,んなことより 燃料が切れちまったんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.94,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Anywhere we can go to refill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.94,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どっかで補給できねか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.10,Default,nick,0,0,0,,You know about Prohibition, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:21.10,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,お前 禁酒法って知ってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.60,Default,nick,0,0,0,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.60,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,知らねぇようならだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.55,Default,nick,0,0,0,,Try the drug store up the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.55,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,この先のドラッグストアに行ってみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.55,Default,nick,0,0,0,,Tell them Nick sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.55,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,ニックから聞いたってなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.47,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.47,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.04,Default,nick,0,0,0,,I don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.04,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,タバコはやらない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What an tacky wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.31,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,悪趣味な財布だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.73,Default,hun,0,0,0,,Hey! Sorry to bother you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.73,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,おい 突然ですまねが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.90,Default,hun,0,0,0,,but I could really use your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:04.90,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,ちょっと 手を貸してもらえると助けるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.05,Default,hun,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.05,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,この野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.30,Default,hun,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.30,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,覚えとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.18,Default,hun,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.18,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:22.00,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah, we just got to a town called Khota.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:22.00,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,うん 今コタって町についたところが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.07,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don't stay too long in any one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.07,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,余り一か所に長居するなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.61,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We only just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.61,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,つい先 来たばっかだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:32.45,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I'm saying that Orco has \Nsent someone after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:32.45,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,いや お前らにオルコから追っ手がかかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.40,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ガンゾが仕入れた話じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:37.93,Default,bar,0,0,0,,From what Ganzo found out, \Nhe's a big man, a regular Goliath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.93,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ゴリアテ見たいな大男だし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.85,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Goliath?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.85,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ゴリアテ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.69,Default,bar,0,0,0,,A giant from the Old Testament. \NNine feet, six inches tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.69,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,旧約聖書に出てくる9フィート6インチの巨人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.12,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Couldn't you pick a less confusing example?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.12,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,分かり辛い喩だなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.58,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don't you ever read your Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.88,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,聖書ぐらい読んでおけ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:52.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I haven't exactly had time to go to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:52.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,教会に通うほど暇じゃなかったんでな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.52,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Well, if I see a big guy, I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まあ でかいのを見かけたら 気を付けるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.94,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Oh, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.94,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,あ 後は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.86,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We've got trouble on the \Nhorizon with Fango and Orco.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.86,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ファンゴとオルコがきな臭いことになってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.71,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.71,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,だろうなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,You can't keep a collar on that mad dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,あの狂犬に首輪は嵌めらんねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.67,Default,nero,0,0,0,,No matter who the master is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.67,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どんな飼い主でもなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.49,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Give me your hardest stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.49,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,一番きつい奴くれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.75,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まあ こんなもんか?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.32,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Keep it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.32,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おかわりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.14,Default,nick,0,0,0,,Shut your dog up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.14,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,こいつを黙らせてやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.31,Default,nick,0,0,0,,That's the fine for barking \Nat law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.31,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,保安官様に吠えた罰金だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.99,Default,nick,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. Got some good stuff here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.99,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,いかんな 上物か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.17,Default,mm,0,0,0,,Seen anyone new in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:18.17,通用720日文-ja,mm,0,0,0,,旅行者を見たか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.70,Default,mm,0,0,0,,Two young men traveling together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.70,通用720日文-ja,mm,0,0,0,,二人組の若い男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.41,Default,nick,0,0,0,,I... I have! I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.41,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,見た 見た
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.63,Default,nick,0,0,0,,At the drug store... Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.63,通用720日文-ja,nick,0,0,0,,ドラッグストアだ 放せ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.75,Default,mm,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.75,通用720日文-ja,mm,0,0,0,,放して
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.46,Default,mm,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.46,通用720日文-ja,mm,0,0,0,,嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.29,Default,man,0,0,0,,Not bad, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.29,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,やるなぁ 兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.35,Default,man,0,0,0,,He won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.35,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,また勝ちやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.76,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:09.76,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,まずい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.04,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Big Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.04,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ビッグメヒコ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.58,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, Señor! Let's have a round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.58,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,セニョール 一丁やるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.91,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone. Place your bets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.91,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,よし みんな 賭けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.03,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Come on, bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.03,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ほら 来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.32,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm sobering up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.32,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,酔いが冷めちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.32,Default,mm,0,0,0,,Stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.32,通用720日文-ja,mm,0,0,0,,くせぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.26,Default,man,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.26,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.66,Default,man,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.66,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,Sounds lively in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.34,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,賑やかだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,The fun's just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.20,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,お楽しみはこれからだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.06,Default,av,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.06,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.01,Default,av,0,0,0,,We're in no position to be \Nplaying around in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.01,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,俺たちは大っぴらに遊べる立場じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.82,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sorry to cut the fun short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.82,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,白けさせて 悪かったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.27,Default,mm,0,0,0,,Stinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.27,通用720日文-ja,mm,0,0,0,,くせぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.82,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I see your practice paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.82,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,練習してきた甲斐があったな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:47.95,Overlap,man,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:47.95,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,{\an8}大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.70,Overlap,man,0,0,0,,C-Call a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.70,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,{\an8}医 医者を呼べ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.70,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.47,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:51.47,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,早く出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:16.00,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We're so far out in the sticks, \Nwe can't even hitchhike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:16.00,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ド田舎過ぎてヒッチハイクもできあしねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.02,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,あれはどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.77,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.18,Default,av,0,0,0,,You really think he'll come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:21.18,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,本当に来るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.80,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.80,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,多分なぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:26.29,Default,nero,0,0,0,,That dog he had was a skilled scent hound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:26.29,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,連れてる犬は凄腕のセントハウンドだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.02,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.02,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なんだこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.24,Default,av,0,0,0,,Canned goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.24,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,缶詰だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.38,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,見りゃ分かる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:52.46,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I can see that. Are you making \Na pineapple cake or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.46,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,パイナップルケーキでも作んのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.67,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey. Quit messing around and oil the guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.67,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,おぃ 遊んでないで 銃の手入れしとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.02,Default,av,0,0,0,,I forgot them in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.02,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,車に忘れた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:02.28,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What? If you're gonna forget \Nsomething, forget this stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:02.28,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,はぁ どうせならこっち忘れて来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.65,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.65,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,腹減った
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.81,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.81,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.08,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Go ahead! Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.08,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ほら かかってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.74,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I guess you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.74,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,貸しができたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:41.70,Default,av,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:41.70,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,なにが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.15,Default,nero,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:44.15,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,なにがって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.20,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I just saved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.20,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,今助けてやっただろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.56,Default,av,0,0,0,,You should be thanking me, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.80,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,それを言うなら俺の方が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.60,通用720日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.87,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. We're—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.87,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,待ってくれ 俺たち...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.70,Default,hun,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.70,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:56.79,Default,hun,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:56.79,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,動くんじゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.16,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.71,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,化け物め 化け物め
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:03.71,Default,hun,0,0,0,,You damn monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.95,Default,hun,0,0,0,,Who the hell was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.95,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,なんなんだ此奴は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:20.51,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Gorillath.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:20.51,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ゴリラテだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:21.56,Default,hun,0,0,0,,Gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:21.56,通用720日文-ja,hun,0,0,0,,ゴリラ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:24.27,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Read your Bible sometime, old man.
